{"tid":1378144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係無線新聞做既屋企人話杯葛黃金時段廣告對袁志偉不痛不癢","createTime":"2019-07-28T15:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T00:21:19.000Z","uid":151365,"like":96,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4a3454fcaced18cea85bc063e66d6a9a8d9bc837","tid":1378144,"uid":151365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:18:01.000Z","msg":"今日問佢點解袁志偉咁樣比人追擊法都咩事都無<br />\n討論起黎先發現大家錯左焦點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解袁志偉會可以無事，政治立場固然係其中一個原因<br />\n但更大原因係因為係佢管治下 <span style=\"color: red;\">公認係燒錢既電視台新聞部 可以賺到錢</span><br />\n新聞部點賺錢? 就係靠袁志偉R sponsor 拍節目 例如睇樓節目<br />\n而且新聞部400人做梗兩條頻道 叫做相當高效率<br />\n就憑以上兩點 李寶安實會睇住佢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以如果想袁志偉下台 其實應該針對返佢幫TVB R返黎既財路</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7582ee286cbfca146ce3fcdfa6d7af20dc105323","tid":1378144,"uid":151365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:19:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5ec2f078fd5766c0b5202226007651ae1510e7d","tid":1378144,"uid":151365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.